title: TOO OLD TOO FAT LANCE & CHA PART
description:
The filmer part to bring you back down to earth after Donny's part!

*editor's note: Adam's footage is extra impressive when you know that a majority of his clips were shot after pulling all nighters frmo partying the night before. He parties like he's in his  twenties.
